## PE7 CSS (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- OKLCH only — no hex/hsl/rgb
- `@layer`: reset/tokens/base/layout/components/animations
- Logical properties only (inline/block, never left/right/top/bottom)
- Native CSS nesting — no SCSS/LESS
- Design tokens in `:root` — colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows
- `var(--dur-*)` + `var(--ease-*)` for transitions
- No Tailwind/UnoCSS/Windi · No clsx/cn()
- Scoped `<style>` per component · Global only in layout tokens
- `class` arrays/objects for conditionals (replaces `class:` directive)
- `<Child --color="red" />` for cross-component styling
- `style:--columns={columns}` for JS-driven values
- `:global` scoping for child overrides when custom properties aren't enough

